As the Autobots and Maximals exchanged greetings with the newest
prime, Legacy continued his quick walk through the old Maximal base,
quickly arriving at the location where Nightstrike was being held.
Entering a series of commands the door opened and Legacy looked
around, his single optic pulsing for a moment.

Stepping in to the room he quickly checked on Nightstrike's vitals to
ensure that the minion was indeed still alive. With a small nod of
satisfaction he waited for the  others to arrive.

(OOC: Anyone know where Nightstrike was held?)

Preston
